Raw kyren fish (6) is a type of fish obtained from fishing spots within the Chambers of Xeric. Raw kyren fish require level 90 in Fishing to catch and grants the player 38 experience when caught.

They are cooked with a Cooking level of 90 to produce kyren fish (6), granting 28 experience in Cooking.
